('exhibitor','index','profile','descArtist','<p class=\"p1\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\">In the Description section below, briefly describe your art so we may locate your display to best highlight it. Please be sure to include any special display requirements (over-sized work, electricity, floor space, co-locate with another artist, etc.). We will do our best to accommodate these requirements.</p>'),
