('portal','accountSettings','main','bottom','Controll-Default: This is portal-accountSettings-main-bottom<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','accountSettings','main','identities','<p>If you have multiple email addresses, and do not want to have to remember which one you used to create your account, you may add the others here to link them. You may also delete any accounts you no longer use.<br><br>There are two ways to login to the registration portal.<br>If you wish to login using the \"Email with Authentication\" method, leave the provider space blank. You will receive an email with a link to login and confirm.<br>If you wish to login using Google, type \"google\" in the provider space. You will receive an email now to login and confirm, but in the future can use your Google account to login.</p>'),
('portal','accountSettings','main','managed','<p>Below is the list of accounts that you manage. To remove an account, click \"remove.\" You may use the form below to add additional account. The person giving you permission to manage their account will need to provide you with their account ID and email address associated with the account.</p>'),
('portal','accountSettings','main','passkeys','<p>A quicker and more secure way to login into your account is by using a passkey.</p><p>Passkeys are a public-key encryption system to securely identify you and require some sort of identification before they can be used. Passkeys can be held in your browser, synced to the cloud, or stored in your password manager.</p><p>Passkeys are an immediate form of login. No waiting for a token to arrive in the email or a 2FA verification code to be sent to your phone or email account.</p><p>In this section you can create a new passkey, or delete an existing one.  You may have as many different passkeys as you wish, but each will be\nyou</p>'),
('portal','accountSettings','main','top','Controll-Default: This is portal-accountSettings-main-top<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','add','email','after','Controll-Default: This is portal-add-email-after<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the ConTroll Admin App under RegAdmin/Edit Custom Text.<br/>Default text display can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','add','email','before','Controll-Default: This is portal-add-email-before<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the ConTroll Admin App under RegAdmin/Edit Custom Text.<br/>Default text display can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','add','profile','bottom','Controll-Default: This is portal-add-profile-bottom<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the ConTroll Admin App under RegAdmin/Edit Custom Text.<br/>Default text display can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','add','profile','top','Controll-Default: This is portal-add-profile-top<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the ConTroll Admin App under RegAdmin/Edit Custom Text.<br/>Default text display can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','all','footer','difficulties','For any difficulties with the registration system please contact registration at\n            <a href=\"mailto:#regadminemail#?subject=Portal%20Difficulties\">#regadminemail#</a>'),
('portal','cart','main','bottom','Controll-Default: This is portal-addUpgrade-main-bottom<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','cart','main','cart','Controll-Default: This is portal-addUpgrade-main-step4bottom<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','cart','main','memberships','<p>This is where you may purchase memberships,&nbsp; upgrade your current membership and make donations and and any other special Membership     offerings.</p>\n<p>Note: To buy a Child or Kid In Tow membership you must have an over 18 membership already in your account.</p>'),
('portal','cart','main','top','Controll-Default: This is portal-addUpgrade-main-top<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','index','main','bottom','Controll-Default: This is portal-index-main-bottom<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','index','main','multiple','Controll-Default: This is portal-index-main-multiple<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','index','main','notloggedin','<p>If you don&rsquo;t already have an account, the next screen will say: &ldquo;The email (your email address) does not have an account&rdquo; and we will take you through the steps of creating an account.</p>\n<p>This is our way of asking &ldquo;Are you sure this is the correct email?&rdquo; If you&rsquo;re sure then go ahead and create your account.</p>\n<p>You will need to create a minimal account for yourself even if you are just buying a membership for someone else if you want to receive a valid receipt for your payment.</p>'),
('portal','index','main','top','Controll-Default: This is portal-index-main-top<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','index','profile','bottom','Controll-Default: This is portal-index-profile-bottom<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the ConTroll Admin App under RegAdmin/Edit Custom Text.<br/>Default text display can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','index','profile','email','<p><br>An email address is required for portal access. If the person you are adding does not have their own email you may use your email.</p>'),
('portal','index','profile','top','Controll-Default: This is portal-index-profile-top<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the ConTroll Admin App under RegAdmin/Edit Custom Text.<br/>Default text display can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','membershipHistory','main','bottom','Controll-Default: This is portal-membershipHistory-main-bottom<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','membershipHistory','main','top','Controll-Default: This is portal-membershipHistory-main-top<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','portal','main','bottom','Controll-Default: This is portal-portal-main-bottom<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','portal','main','changeEmail','<p>You can only change your accounts email address to an email address in your identities in Account Settings. Please use the \"Add New\" button to add any new email addresses to your account. Identities is only available in Account Settings once your account has been assigned an ID and is no longer pending.</p>\n<p>You can only change the email address for an account you manage to one of your own (as above) or to one of the email addresses of people you manage.</p>\n<p>If you need to make any other changes, please contact registration at registration2025@philcon.org and ask for assistance.</p>'),
('portal','portal','main','people','<p><strong>To buy a membership</strong> click on Add To/Edit Cart next to the name.<br><strong>To request information</strong> about such things as art show, dealers room, volunteering, etc, click \"Edit (Name\'s) Interests\"</p>'),
('portal','portal','main','plan','Controll-Default: This is portal-portal-main-plan<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','portal','main','purchased','Controll-Default: This is portal-portal-main-purchased<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','portal','main','purchOthers','Controll-Default: This is portal-portal-main-purchOthers<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('portal','portal','main','top','Controll-Default: This is portal-portal-main-top<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('profile','all','interests','footer','Controll-Default: This is profile-all-interests-footer<br/>Custom HTML that can replaced with a custom value in the Controll Admin App under Edit Custom Text.<br/> Default text can be suppressed in the configuration file.'),
('profile','all','interests','header','<span class=\"size-h3\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Additional Interests or Needs</span>\n<p>This form lets us know if you want to be contacted about specific things. We ask these questions to help us give you the experience you are after.</p>'),
